      "text": "Nakajima Satoru Kanshuu F1 Grand Prix is a 1991 game by Varie for the Sega Mega Drive in their Nakajima Satoru Kanshuu series of Formula One racing games released exclusively in Japan.\n\nThe game is a typical overhead 2D racing game. A accelerates, B brakes, Left and Right seers, and Up and Down change gears.",
